verses.verse: Praise <S%H1984><s%> ye Jehovah <S%H3050><s%>. Praise <S%H1984><s%> God <S%H410><s%> in his sanctuary <S%H6944><s%>: Praise <S%H1984><s%> him in the firmament <S%H7549><s%> of his power <S%H5797><s%>.
Praise <S%H1984><s%> him for his mighty acts <S%H1369><s%>: Praise <S%H1984><s%> him according to his excellent <S%H7230><s%> greatness <S%H1433><s%>.
Praise <S%H1984><s%> him with trumpet <S%H7782><s%> sound <S%H8629><s%>: Praise <S%H1984><s%> him with psaltery <S%H5035><s%> and harp <S%H5035><s%>.
Praise <S%H1984><s%> him with timbrel <S%H8596><s%> and dance <S%H4234><s%>: Praise <S%H1984><s%> him with stringed instruments <S%H4482><s%> and pipe <S%H5748><s%>.
Praise <S%H1984><s%> him with loud <S%H8088><s%> cymbals <S%H6767><s%>: Praise <S%H1984><s%> him with high sounding <S%H8643><s%> cymbals <S%H6767><s%>.
Let everything that hath breath <S%H5397><s%> praise <S%H1984><s%> Jehovah <S%H3050><s%>. Praise <S%H1984><s%> ye Jehovah <S%H3050><s%>.
